text: Jack Newby (born 20 November 1993) is a South African cricketer. He made his Twenty20 cricket debut for Western Province on 4 September 2015 in the 2015 Africa T20 Cup. He made his List A debut for Western Province in the 2017–18 CSA Provincial One-Day Challenge on 11 February 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Western Province cricketers Category:People from Islington (district) Category:Sportspeople from London
